parameters: "Hey, you two. Long time no see.. Wait, you over there, you're a girl?"
"A-Ahaha. Actually, um, there were various circumstances.."

"Since we'll be living together from now on, I hope we can continue to get
along well."

"Oh, oh, you're doing naughty things while trying to look serious.
Congrats. Being young is great, isn't it?"

(Despite their appearance, they seem like a kind person.. Oh, but it's only
Bunno-san who bullies others, and it seems like they want to be bullied
too.. Maybe they're actually a good person at heart?)
"..What do you think of Bunno-san, Sarashina-san?"

"I've been thinking this since the first time I saw you, but your body is
amazing."
(..As I thought, he might not be a very good person.)
共有セーブデータのセーブ
[If you don't mind, please give this to Hinori-san.]

[I apologize for not considering your relationship before. Although it may
not be appropriate to say congratulations on your marriage, it is still
proper to put it in writing.]
"What.. what are you planning to use it for.. ♥"

"Isn't it difficult for you, Fumino-san, to always communicate through
written notes with such beautiful handwriting?"
"[It's not like I do it all the time]"
Ako shyly flips through her notebook and shows it to me.

"At first, most of it was written in beautiful handwriting, but as I
flipped through the pages, I noticed that the letters gradually became
cuter and more playful towards the end."

(..It's kind of lewd that you can tell we started doing it around the time
my handwriting started changing.)
